Module it.polimi.ingsw.am11
Package it.polimi.ingsw.am11.view.client.TUI

Class Actuator

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.am11.view.client.TUI.Actuator
public class Actuator extends Object
Its purpose is to effectively actuate the commands parsed by the reader. This is an "intermediate class" between the classes that read input and the interface of the network (CltToNetConnector). It's needed because the connector is not initialized at the beginning of the communication.
